{"tid":1419053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<蘋果> 光復香港　時代革命 - 李怡","createTime":"2019-08-05T23:21:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T19:35:57.000Z","uid":35790,"like":108,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"6f844286e159aaae2b6110f69fc2efbfdaab32fd","tid":1419053,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:21:40.000Z","msg":"世道人生：光復香港　時代革命 - 李怡<br />\r\n<br />\r\n 林鄭指部份示威者令事件變質，污損國徽、拉下國旗扔落海，揚言「搞革命」、「光復香港」等，均是挑戰國家主權、危害一國兩制的行為，會摧毀香港的穩定繁榮。「我哋係咪要押上700萬人的穩定生活、同香港未來作賭注？這種有人形容為『玉石俱焚』嘅做法，會令社會走向不歸路。」<br />\r\n<br />\r\n我想相當多的市民的想法是：送中條例以及接下來的林鄭政權倒行逆施的手段，尤其是7.21元朗事件後，「令事件變質」，示威者重提「光復香港，時代革命」的口號，是因為林鄭的作為已「危害一國兩制」、「會摧毀香港的穩定繁榮」；送中條例堅持不肯用立法會的法定語言「撤回」，讓人感到是要留下後路，重新提出這個犧牲香港700萬人的法律權利的惡法，「押上700萬人的穩定生活、同香港未來」？林鄭一意孤行的作為，把香港年輕人逼至走投無路，被迫走上「玉石俱焚」的「予及汝皆亡」的「不歸路」。面對數人死諫，數以百計的大好青年被打受傷被捕，林鄭殘酷冰涼的心靈居然沒有一點聲響，反而把責任推向保衞香港自由和法律權利的年輕抗爭者。她見傳媒不但沒有澆熄怒火，反而是向市民的怒火澆火水。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n「污損國徽、拉下國旗扔落海」，按美國焚燒國旗的案例，法官認為屬「言論表達自由」的範圍，經典判詞指，美國國旗是「自由信念的標誌」，「因此，這面國旗同時也保護那些藐視它的人！」。中國國旗縱使不是「自由信念的標誌」，但損毀一面國旗如果就能夠「危害一國兩制」，那麼「一國兩制」豈不是太脆弱了？<br />\r\n<br />\r\n事件的確有些變質了。但變質的原因不是示威者造成的，而是政府的應對與鎮壓行動造成的。在反送中的100萬人、200萬人的遊行中，聽不到「光復香港，時代革命」的口號，而在7.21之後，所有境內境外媒體的影片都顯示，元朗警黑配合，事後警方交差式拘捕十來個人，他們持械狂打市民昭昭在目，卻只控以非法集結罪並獲保釋；反而一些證據薄弱的示威者，就控以最重判刑的暴動罪，一些持有微不足道器械的示威者更不獲保釋，還柙至9月。面對這樣的政權，還是原來的香港嗎？還不足以說香港已經淪陷了嗎？中國近年高喊的「復興中華」，沒有人說出是復興到甚麼時代，是暴秦時期還是文革時期？但「光復香港」我們都知道要「光復」到甚麼時代，不就是人權有保障、市民有法律權利、警察是保護市民而不是向自由表達意見的市民施暴的香港嗎？打出港英旗也好，打出美國旗也罷，重點都不是呼喚英國美國來統治香港，而是表示香港要回到英美體制中對自由、對人權的保護。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「時代革命」是革甚麼命？革命的定義就是尋求根本性的改變。革命不一定是改朝換代，不一定是暴力與流血。工業革命，技術革命也是革命。</span></span>文化大革命是在原有朝代中進行，辛亥革命實際上暴力與流血不多，有史家認為暴力與流血比日本的明治維新還少。香港的「時代革命」，就是要把被中共港共徹底破壞了的一國兩制、港人治港作根本性的改變。<br />\n<br />\n香港市民本來沒有想到要作這樣根本性改變的，但7.21讓我們覺得香港變成黑社會統治了，於是即使在和理非的示威中，也喊出了梁天琦2016年的口號：「光復香港，時代革命」！事情的變質是由元朗事件引起的。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190806/20743857\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190806%2F20743857&d=UMlFbumbAr%2BzuUpIk3BrKdAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=70e14057\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190806%2F20743857&h=d2757a6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190806/20743857</a>"},{"pid":"f8980232be998dab52cb97cbb13954648651837c","tid":1419053,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:23:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b7b52373494cb0805d13b6f2bb8e10959d74419","tid":1419053,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:26:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b93b6ff85967b59b8608692b7625867a599431e","tid":1419053,"uid":19847,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:27:31.000Z","msg":"李怡先生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34510efab0cb9aca48e9f9bd02e4bf730e88f349","tid":1419053,"uid":87498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:27:42.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"a1f0c812b1e825b2eaa26916527bafb3791aa0a1","tid":1419053,"uid":158546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:28:05.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd77e78a3d660de522a93e5010eb272298136a12","tid":1419053,"uid":267078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:31:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf4046a5ec3eaf0b8e795e1e949bc6cdc4b677e","tid":1419053,"uid":193233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:33:03.000Z","msg":"光復香港！時代革命！推比更多人睇"},{"pid":"5c35186467042df9618426fc97c6f5483376db1b","tid":1419053,"uid":135274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:33:48.000Z","msg":"李怡老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"425f6954c6c7f8040165e279efcafd59944985b4","tid":1419053,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:36:34.000Z","msg":"Aggre"},{"pid":"d6e489a1fe10a23b23769f66aeedc49836e9e608","tid":1419053,"uid":237517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:37:19.000Z","msg":"李怡先生確係堅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce97c58eecbe979077cd7ab974f00eb597a7ac78","tid":1419053,"uid":174283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:38:40.000Z","msg":"連李怡都無割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9729a208cabbe4a125948e1b77d9769d6efe911","tid":1419053,"uid":80303,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:38:44.000Z","msg":"各位記唔記得大家出嚟係為咗啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地咁辛苦 咁頻密咁出嚟<br />\n唔係為咗cosplay 著曬full gear 然後坐喺到un un 腳㩒電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亦都唔係為咗食煙 食彈 唔走 等被人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更加唔係為咗要禁止他人發聲 街坊講咗少少嘢唔啱聽就屌人 打人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地出嚟嘅初心 <br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">係為咗對抗哩個腐敗嘅政權 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係為咗追求自由民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有為咗彰顯公義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n我發現 有啲人好熱心咁出嚟 但就忘記咗出嚟嘅初衷⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一 禁止他人影相的人</span></strong><br />\n點解我地一開始唔比人影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為驚黑警認得出你係邊個 然後拉你<br />\n<br />\n不過香港係無肖像權嘅 每個人都有影相嘅自由<br />\n如果因為人地影相而屌人<br />\n咁同吉野家因為一句「撕紙狗」而炒人有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係剝奪咗一啲與生俱來嘅自由<br />\n如果唔想被人影到 應該要遮好自己啲特徵<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>然後客氣咁講「記得唔好影人地嘅大頭啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n而唔係「咪影相啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">二 打深藍街坊的人</span></strong><br />\n好明顯 深藍街坊 係反對我地集會、遊行嘅<br />\n就好似我地反對港共政權一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果我地因為佢地講嘢唔啱聽而打人<br />\n咁同黑警向和平集會嘅人放煙又咩分別呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪一樣都係打壓緊言論自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實佢地話你 你圍住佢唱生日歌 或者話返佢咪夠囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>如果佢地唔係主動出手 做咩要傷害佢地呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">三 阻止手足去制服黑社會的人</span></strong><br />\n我地出嚟 係因為官、警、商、黑勾結啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑社會係無性㗎 佢地唔會同你講道理㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地根本就有曬準備 見人就打<br />\n一個唔好彩被佢打到 真係要住成個月醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你哩刻放佢走 佢轉頭打第二個㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你以為你救緊人？其實你係害緊你的手足啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺哩個社會 黑警同法律已經制裁唔到佢地<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>如果義士都唔做嘢<br />\n你覺得有咩人先可以令佢地得到應有嘅懲罰呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">四 胡亂起火的人</span></strong><br />\n火之所以危險 唔只係因為佢熱<br />\n更加係因為佢好難控制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似尖沙咀咁 燒燒吓無啦啦有個小爆炸<br />\n如果個爆炸係喺路障果到發生 燒到自己人點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要啲火係會驚動到真・消防嚟救熄 增加佢地嘅工作量<br />\n所以大家喺點火之前 記得諗吓佢有冇實質作用（你懂的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n如果你做嘅嘢係有意義、有功用 而又唔會傷害到<span style=\"color: red;\">自己人</span>嘅話<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>相信你做咩都唔會有人阻止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">五 極度膽小的前線</span></strong><br />\n如果你咁容易驚 點解唔留喺中線、後線呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有好多時候 得幾隻速龍埋嚟<br />\n又或者根本連條狗毛都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前排嘅人就好驚咁向後跑<br />\n連帶後面啲人都跟住跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做成不必要嘅混亂 影響軍心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>如果你咁易驚 不如試吓其他崗位<br />\n可能有更大嘅作為都唔定呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">六 唔識判斷時勢的勇武</span></strong><br />\n出嚟同黑警對峙唔係為咗被人拉啊<br />\n而係要比壓力佢地同埋政府啊<br />\n如果你被人拉咗 我地又點會比到壓力佢地呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做得勇武 掟得雞蛋 你就要識判斷時勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要知道你可以衝到幾前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要知道啲狗幾時會放屁 咬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你判斷錯咗 咁就被人拉㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日話be water be water <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果你唔知個風吹邊面 又點樣若水呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">七 作假標題開po嘅人</span></strong><br />\n其實你開po 都係想表達你嘅所思所想姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為咗令多啲人睇你個po 為咗多啲留言<br />\n而作個同你嘅內文不符嘅假標題<br />\n其實係表達唔到你真正想講嘅嘢㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更甚嘅係 當大家都出咗去嘅時候<br />\n真係唔會有時間禁入去睇你嘅長篇大論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能只係會掃吓熱門嘅標題<br />\n略略知道各個地方發生咩事 睇吓邊到需要支援<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>你個假標題係有機會做成混亂㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 知唔知</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有啲方法可能係以前work 而家唔work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但亦都可能調返轉 以前唔work 而家work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯獨一樣嘢 係一直無變嘅<br />\n就係我地出嚟嘅<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">最終目的</span></strong>啊<br />\n咁多位手足 試下花少少時間諗清楚<br />\n我地做嘅每一樣嘢 係為咗啲乜 好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">對準腐敗政權 實現五大訴求<br />\n不割𥱊 不篤灰 不分化 不被捕</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話：<br />\n黑警想盡辦法令記者影唔到相 成件事會對抗爭運動好不利<br />\n攝影最基本嘅條件係光<br />\n本身街燈啲光已經唔適合影相 熄埋街燈就仲絕<br />\n各位手足真係要諗辦法搞搞佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"c0f016ab330f7defb3d094cff41d6ae4bf5286ae","tid":1419053,"uid":105130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:39:08.000Z","msg":"「革命」唔一定係用武力推翻政權<br />\n<br />\n可以係政治制度嘅徹底改革"},{"pid":"abb4b04cc8aae7019e932d35f760441607734e04","tid":1419053,"uid":289897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebac406a280993d56c7b0e13f7fd6928a25cdab8","tid":1419053,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:42:35.000Z","msg":"光復香港  時代革命<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5aea19f2c9f6c57f20d5034e2e7cafc58b714d9","tid":1419053,"uid":271241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:42:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a4f576105c02ad959759aa9e28daf842b7ca184","tid":1419053,"uid":127988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0f016ab330f7defb3d094cff41d6ae4bf5286ae","tid":1419053,"uid":105130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:39:08.000Z","msg":"「革命」唔一定係用武力推翻政權<br />\n<br />\n可以係政治制度嘅徹底改革"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:43:21.000Z","msg":"香港啟蒙運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1067e4c8f406dd98d8937661c534e7f0e26ad2a8","tid":1419053,"uid":37396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:48:12.000Z","msg":"李怡bb <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ce143cb41d070696acf152c1bb9946c27215edf","tid":1419053,"uid":96964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:49:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"24564d414f0c0f39a8f773da5f8b4bb6334c1be5","tid":1419053,"uid":37504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:50:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b9ffd17d97ab7a9f011198e11aa1a840788fae9","tid":1419053,"uid":289081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f9729a208cabbe4a125948e1b77d9769d6efe911","tid":1419053,"uid":80303,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:38:44.000Z","msg":"各位記唔記得大家出嚟係為咗啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地咁辛苦 咁頻密咁出嚟<br />\n唔係為咗cosplay 著曬full gear 然後坐喺到un un 腳㩒電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亦都唔係為咗食煙 食彈 唔走 等被人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更加唔係為咗要禁止他人發聲 街坊講咗少少嘢唔啱聽就屌人 打人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地出嚟嘅初心 <br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">係為咗對抗哩個腐敗嘅政權 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係為咗追求自由民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有為咗彰顯公義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n我發現 有啲人好熱心咁出嚟 但就忘記咗出嚟嘅初衷⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一 禁止他人影相的人</span></strong><br />\n點解我地一開始唔比人影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為驚黑警認得出你係邊個 然後拉你<br />\n<br />\n不過香港係無肖像權嘅 每個人都有影相嘅自由<br />\n如果因為人地影相而屌人<br />\n咁同吉野家因為一句「撕紙狗」而炒人有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係剝奪咗一啲與生俱來嘅自由<br />\n如果唔想被人影到 應該要遮好自己啲特徵<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>然後客氣咁講「記得唔好影人地嘅大頭啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n而唔係「咪影相啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">二 打深藍街坊的人</span></strong><br />\n好明顯 深藍街坊 係反對我地集會、遊行嘅<br />\n就好似我地反對港共政權一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果我地因為佢地講嘢唔啱聽而打人<br />\n咁同黑警向和平集會嘅人放煙又咩分別呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪一樣都係打壓緊言論自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實佢地話你 你圍住佢唱生日歌 或者話返佢咪夠囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>如果佢地唔係主動出手 做咩要傷害佢地呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">三 阻止手足去制服黑社會的人</span></strong><br />\n我地出嚟 係因為官、警、商、黑勾結啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑社會係無性㗎 佢地唔會同你講道理㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地根本就有曬準備 見人就打<br />\n一個唔好彩被佢打到 真係要住成個月醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你哩刻放佢走 佢轉頭打第二個㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你以為你救緊人？其實你係害緊你的手足啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺哩個社會 黑警同法律已經制裁唔到佢地<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>如果義士都唔做嘢<br />\n你覺得有咩人先可以令佢地得到應有嘅懲罰呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">四 胡亂起火的人</span></strong><br />\n火之所以危險 唔只係因為佢熱<br />\n更加係因為佢好難控制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似尖沙咀咁 燒燒吓無啦啦有個小爆炸<br />\n如果個爆炸係喺路障果到發生 燒到自己人點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要啲火係會驚動到真・消防嚟救熄 增加佢地嘅工作量<br />\n所以大家喺點火之前 記得諗吓佢有冇實質作用（你懂的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n如果你做嘅嘢係有意義、有功用 而又唔會傷害到<span style=\"color: red;\">自己人</span>嘅話<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>相信你做咩都唔會有人阻止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">五 極度膽小的前線</span></strong><br />\n如果你咁容易驚 點解唔留喺中線、後線呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有好多時候 得幾隻速龍埋嚟<br />\n又或者根本連條狗毛都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前排嘅人就好驚咁向後跑<br />\n連帶後面啲人都跟住跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做成不必要嘅混亂 影響軍心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>如果你咁易驚 不如試吓其他崗位<br />\n可能有更大嘅作為都唔定呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">六 唔識判斷時勢的勇武</span></strong><br />\n出嚟同黑警對峙唔係為咗被人拉啊<br />\n而係要比壓力佢地同埋政府啊<br />\n如果你被人拉咗 我地又點會比到壓力佢地呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做得勇武 掟得雞蛋 你就要識判斷時勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要知道你可以衝到幾前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要知道啲狗幾時會放屁 咬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你判斷錯咗 咁就被人拉㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日話be water be water <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果你唔知個風吹邊面 又點樣若水呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">七 作假標題開po嘅人</span></strong><br />\n其實你開po 都係想表達你嘅所思所想姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為咗令多啲人睇你個po 為咗多啲留言<br />\n而作個同你嘅內文不符嘅假標題<br />\n其實係表達唔到你真正想講嘅嘢㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更甚嘅係 當大家都出咗去嘅時候<br />\n真係唔會有時間禁入去睇你嘅長篇大論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能只係會掃吓熱門嘅標題<br />\n略略知道各個地方發生咩事 睇吓邊到需要支援<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>你個假標題係有機會做成混亂㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 知唔知</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有啲方法可能係以前work 而家唔work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但亦都可能調返轉 以前唔work 而家work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯獨一樣嘢 係一直無變嘅<br />\n就係我地出嚟嘅<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">最終目的</span></strong>啊<br />\n咁多位手足 試下花少少時間諗清楚<br />\n我地做嘅每一樣嘢 係為咗啲乜 好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">對準腐敗政權 實現五大訴求<br />\n不割𥱊 不篤灰 不分化 不被捕</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話：<br />\n黑警想盡辦法令記者影唔到相 成件事會對抗爭運動好不利<br />\n攝影最基本嘅條件係光<br />\n本身街燈啲光已經唔適合影相 熄埋街燈就仲絕<br />\n各位手足真係要諗辦法搞搞佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:53:46.000Z","msg":"痴撚線！呢篇嘢做乜擺回應到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n開個新post啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n心聲呀屌！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"32c01da966ade12fad047bec262603baefb01729","tid":1419053,"uid":8577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:56:26.000Z","msg":"光復香港！時代革命！<br />\n<br />\n尋日連登收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想個口號冇人嗌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3970f60642c3aa4f898d554019fc780c76c72a0","tid":1419053,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:04:24.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"d35c37c444af0cbcfe5a459821cf8b340ccb759b","tid":1419053,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:23:04.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"73d763ce7d5c607f8ae6f6b3ae54fbc0513ff77c","tid":1419053,"uid":260037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:30:59.000Z","msg":"講得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad1cd957f91cb87eadd07d4dd70838d3acc0d47f","tid":1419053,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:33:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"82da329e21597d709de0c8f5a305b37bb4529a0e","tid":1419053,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:49:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a4cf7fba730fdd8875c6d5abae89261beba48137","tid":1419053,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:58:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"476daa3143073b3dc638f2064bd6ee5d52a8a0dc","tid":1419053,"uid":7484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:10:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dfa93101920f4599877c230665ae0a72cdd47a53","tid":1419053,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:16:46.000Z","msg":"推啊屌"},{"pid":"4e2f29687350a9c8e203cdbfbf4223502f684941","tid":1419053,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:22:19.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"d6af9d95927bff4c19d34126ca2666d58c61ebcb","tid":1419053,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:23:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68d09eb5b112bab7bb5a38516bb3bc5acdfbd4db","tid":1419053,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:24:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013893785fe37fad72b9684a305cc705a908093b","tid":1419053,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:24:59.000Z","msg":"李怡先生都唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"576ed24420be7e86b5e97ddf005f35984e477661","tid":1419053,"uid":29302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:27:53.000Z","msg":"用黎做文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f75baab190f2d8c61545a7c49b63d721a5893a56","tid":1419053,"uid":291911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:28:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1787f51ea83de5790afc7771042ae34bcb50db08","tid":1419053,"uid":191656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9729a208cabbe4a125948e1b77d9769d6efe911","tid":1419053,"uid":80303,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:38:44.000Z","msg":"各位記唔記得大家出嚟係為咗啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地咁辛苦 咁頻密咁出嚟<br />\n唔係為咗cosplay 著曬full gear 然後坐喺到un un 腳㩒電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亦都唔係為咗食煙 食彈 唔走 等被人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更加唔係為咗要禁止他人發聲 街坊講咗少少嘢唔啱聽就屌人 打人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地出嚟嘅初心 <br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">係為咗對抗哩個腐敗嘅政權 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係為咗追求自由民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有為咗彰顯公義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n我發現 有啲人好熱心咁出嚟 但就忘記咗出嚟嘅初衷⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一 禁止他人影相的人</span></strong><br />\n點解我地一開始唔比人影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為驚黑警認得出你係邊個 然後拉你<br />\n<br />\n不過香港係無肖像權嘅 每個人都有影相嘅自由<br />\n如果因為人地影相而屌人<br />\n咁同吉野家因為一句「撕紙狗」而炒人有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係剝奪咗一啲與生俱來嘅自由<br />\n如果唔想被人影到 應該要遮好自己啲特徵<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>然後客氣咁講「記得唔好影人地嘅大頭啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n而唔係「咪影相啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">二 打深藍街坊的人</span></strong><br />\n好明顯 深藍街坊 係反對我地集會、遊行嘅<br />\n就好似我地反對港共政權一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果我地因為佢地講嘢唔啱聽而打人<br />\n咁同黑警向和平集會嘅人放煙又咩分別呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪一樣都係打壓緊言論自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實佢地話你 你圍住佢唱生日歌 或者話返佢咪夠囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>如果佢地唔係主動出手 做咩要傷害佢地呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">三 阻止手足去制服黑社會的人</span></strong><br />\n我地出嚟 係因為官、警、商、黑勾結啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑社會係無性㗎 佢地唔會同你講道理㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地根本就有曬準備 見人就打<br />\n一個唔好彩被佢打到 真係要住成個月醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你哩刻放佢走 佢轉頭打第二個㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你以為你救緊人？其實你係害緊你的手足啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺哩個社會 黑警同法律已經制裁唔到佢地<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>如果義士都唔做嘢<br />\n你覺得有咩人先可以令佢地得到應有嘅懲罰呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">四 胡亂起火的人</span></strong><br />\n火之所以危險 唔只係因為佢熱<br />\n更加係因為佢好難控制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似尖沙咀咁 燒燒吓無啦啦有個小爆炸<br />\n如果個爆炸係喺路障果到發生 燒到自己人點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要啲火係會驚動到真・消防嚟救熄 增加佢地嘅工作量<br />\n所以大家喺點火之前 記得諗吓佢有冇實質作用（你懂的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n如果你做嘅嘢係有意義、有功用 而又唔會傷害到<span style=\"color: red;\">自己人</span>嘅話<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>相信你做咩都唔會有人阻止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">五 極度膽小的前線</span></strong><br />\n如果你咁容易驚 點解唔留喺中線、後線呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有好多時候 得幾隻速龍埋嚟<br />\n又或者根本連條狗毛都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前排嘅人就好驚咁向後跑<br />\n連帶後面啲人都跟住跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做成不必要嘅混亂 影響軍心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>如果你咁易驚 不如試吓其他崗位<br />\n可能有更大嘅作為都唔定呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">六 唔識判斷時勢的勇武</span></strong><br />\n出嚟同黑警對峙唔係為咗被人拉啊<br />\n而係要比壓力佢地同埋政府啊<br />\n如果你被人拉咗 我地又點會比到壓力佢地呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做得勇武 掟得雞蛋 你就要識判斷時勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要知道你可以衝到幾前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要知道啲狗幾時會放屁 咬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你判斷錯咗 咁就被人拉㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日話be water be water <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果你唔知個風吹邊面 又點樣若水呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">七 作假標題開po嘅人</span></strong><br />\n其實你開po 都係想表達你嘅所思所想姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為咗令多啲人睇你個po 為咗多啲留言<br />\n而作個同你嘅內文不符嘅假標題<br />\n其實係表達唔到你真正想講嘅嘢㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更甚嘅係 當大家都出咗去嘅時候<br />\n真係唔會有時間禁入去睇你嘅長篇大論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能只係會掃吓熱門嘅標題<br />\n略略知道各個地方發生咩事 睇吓邊到需要支援<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>你個假標題係有機會做成混亂㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 知唔知</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有啲方法可能係以前work 而家唔work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但亦都可能調返轉 以前唔work 而家work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯獨一樣嘢 係一直無變嘅<br />\n就係我地出嚟嘅<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">最終目的</span></strong>啊<br />\n咁多位手足 試下花少少時間諗清楚<br />\n我地做嘅每一樣嘢 係為咗啲乜 好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">對準腐敗政權 實現五大訴求<br />\n不割𥱊 不篤灰 不分化 不被捕</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話：<br />\n黑警想盡辦法令記者影唔到相 成件事會對抗爭運動好不利<br />\n攝影最基本嘅條件係光<br />\n本身街燈啲光已經唔適合影相 熄埋街燈就仲絕<br />\n各位手足真係要諗辦法搞搞佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:29:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e46c6a526a7230271cd8a05a5351d3bcdb1134e0","tid":1419053,"uid":283826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:15:43.000Z","msg":"李怡先生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> define返個口號，改革警隊腐敗、和黑社會勾結問題，就是一場革命"},{"pid":"2bf59a2a8d049e84e5a060e54c26fa8998a4fd3a","tid":1419053,"uid":272976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f844286e159aaae2b6110f69fc2efbfdaab32fd","tid":1419053,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:21:40.000Z","msg":"世道人生：光復香港　時代革命 - 李怡<br />\r\n<br />\r\n 林鄭指部份示威者令事件變質，污損國徽、拉下國旗扔落海，揚言「搞革命」、「光復香港」等，均是挑戰國家主權、危害一國兩制的行為，會摧毀香港的穩定繁榮。「我哋係咪要押上700萬人的穩定生活、同香港未來作賭注？這種有人形容為『玉石俱焚』嘅做法，會令社會走向不歸路。」<br />\r\n<br />\r\n我想相當多的市民的想法是：送中條例以及接下來的林鄭政權倒行逆施的手段，尤其是7.21元朗事件後，「令事件變質」，示威者重提「光復香港，時代革命」的口號，是因為林鄭的作為已「危害一國兩制」、「會摧毀香港的穩定繁榮」；送中條例堅持不肯用立法會的法定語言「撤回」，讓人感到是要留下後路，重新提出這個犧牲香港700萬人的法律權利的惡法，「押上700萬人的穩定生活、同香港未來」？林鄭一意孤行的作為，把香港年輕人逼至走投無路，被迫走上「玉石俱焚」的「予及汝皆亡」的「不歸路」。面對數人死諫，數以百計的大好青年被打受傷被捕，林鄭殘酷冰涼的心靈居然沒有一點聲響，反而把責任推向保衞香港自由和法律權利的年輕抗爭者。她見傳媒不但沒有澆熄怒火，反而是向市民的怒火澆火水。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n「污損國徽、拉下國旗扔落海」，按美國焚燒國旗的案例，法官認為屬「言論表達自由」的範圍，經典判詞指，美國國旗是「自由信念的標誌」，「因此，這面國旗同時也保護那些藐視它的人！」。中國國旗縱使不是「自由信念的標誌」，但損毀一面國旗如果就能夠「危害一國兩制」，那麼「一國兩制」豈不是太脆弱了？<br />\r\n<br />\r\n事件的確有些變質了。但變質的原因不是示威者造成的，而是政府的應對與鎮壓行動造成的。在反送中的100萬人、200萬人的遊行中，聽不到「光復香港，時代革命」的口號，而在7.21之後，所有境內境外媒體的影片都顯示，元朗警黑配合，事後警方交差式拘捕十來個人，他們持械狂打市民昭昭在目，卻只控以非法集結罪並獲保釋；反而一些證據薄弱的示威者，就控以最重判刑的暴動罪，一些持有微不足道器械的示威者更不獲保釋，還柙至9月。面對這樣的政權，還是原來的香港嗎？還不足以說香港已經淪陷了嗎？中國近年高喊的「復興中華」，沒有人說出是復興到甚麼時代，是暴秦時期還是文革時期？但「光復香港」我們都知道要「光復」到甚麼時代，不就是人權有保障、市民有法律權利、警察是保護市民而不是向自由表達意見的市民施暴的香港嗎？打出港英旗也好，打出美國旗也罷，重點都不是呼喚英國美國來統治香港，而是表示香港要回到英美體制中對自由、對人權的保護。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「時代革命」是革甚麼命？革命的定義就是尋求根本性的改變。革命不一定是改朝換代，不一定是暴力與流血。工業革命，技術革命也是革命。</span></span>文化大革命是在原有朝代中進行，辛亥革命實際上暴力與流血不多，有史家認為暴力與流血比日本的明治維新還少。香港的「時代革命」，就是要把被中共港共徹底破壞了的一國兩制、港人治港作根本性的改變。<br />\n<br />\n香港市民本來沒有想到要作這樣根本性改變的，但7.21讓我們覺得香港變成黑社會統治了，於是即使在和理非的示威中，也喊出了梁天琦2016年的口號：「光復香港，時代革命」！事情的變質是由元朗事件引起的。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190806/20743857\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190806%2F20743857&d=UMlFbumbAr%2BzuUpIk3BrKdAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=70e14057\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190806%2F20743857&h=d2757a6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190806/20743857</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:17:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b7cb2437d77a119feb0d27373cef2f115405c9b4","tid":1419053,"uid":49643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:27:12.000Z","msg":"一個80幾歲既老人家頭腦仲清晰過班後生好多"},{"pid":"14ffa82c5b34cdb77be947ee30eb459642e05cb6","tid":1419053,"uid":259812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:27:59.000Z","msg":"真係，721連和理非都知道黑警唔再信得過<br />\n政府行動升級係警黑勾結；我地係口號升級<br />\n<br />\n光復香港   時代革命"},{"pid":"7a621739140a5749a26c5201df322da033aea63a","tid":1419053,"uid":106252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:51:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bee30f0ebdffd345d4d556a152de8d8694244c31","tid":1419053,"uid":7534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:52:21.000Z","msg":"八十幾歲嘅李怡頭腦清醒，開明過好多廢中廢藍！就算以前係愛黨愛國一樣可以否定晒過去，呢啲咪有人性囉"},{"pid":"4e8f60cc3b104e5c5e03941042cf6459a2906d3b","tid":1419053,"uid":278431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:16:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88d8ffb59785c8badae5d2cf3b008e330070a8f4","tid":1419053,"uid":49456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:35:09.000Z","msg":"尋日既連登仔<br />\n劉細良？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36400a4acc42b3f8bc03779755f8909a3ad1fd7b","tid":1419053,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:55:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6156452d87ff3fbe7b54380da37bc061c0da6d8d","tid":1419053,"uid":35348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"88d8ffb59785c8badae5d2cf3b008e330070a8f4","tid":1419053,"uid":49456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:35:09.000Z","msg":"尋日既連登仔<br />\n劉細良？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:57:41.000Z","msg":"尋日出面打晒仗 咁得閒開post打長文都知有鬼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae10204a5012d616c9b903cca6671b7fc440a5a1","tid":1419053,"uid":38373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:58:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"083f5bea64ba8f771cf1ee22d4c47cd50d01c31c","tid":1419053,"uid":58670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:58:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}